source_text: Cyprium will receive 1% net smelter royalty on future production from the Cue tenements;
additional_details: Cyprium Metals Ltd (Cyprium) receives the royalty. Q Resources Pty Limited (QR) will be paying it as they acquire the Cue Project. QR has the right to purchase back 50% of the royalty for $500,000 on a public listing of QR.
